/*

ClaimCash AI — Database Schema

Required environ variables:
  DATABASE_URL  — Neon PostgreSQL connection string

Tables:
  - organizations  — multi-company support with Stripe subscription tracking
  - users          — user accounts with role-based access
  - organization_members — many-to-many with roles
  - sessions       — HTTP-only cookie auth sessions
  - contacts       — adjusters, homeowners, commercial, property managers
  - insurance_claims — insurance claim tracking (adjuster details inline)
  - invoices       — main invoice tracking with aging buckets
  - invoice_claims — many-to-many link between invoices and claims
  - collection_tasks — follow-up task management
  - email_templates — reusable email templates for collections
  - audit_log      — full activity trail

To run: bun run src/db/migrate.ts
*/